statements: SELECT * FROM training_datasets;
SELECT dataset_name, dataset_size FROM training_datasets WHERE dataset_id = 1;
SELECT dataset_id, dataset_name FROM training_datasets WHERE dataset_size > 1000 ORDER BY dataset_id DESC;
SELECT dataset_name FROM training_datasets WHERE dataset_format = 'CSV';
SELECT * FROM training_datasets WHERE dataset_size BETWEEN 500 AND 2000 ORDER BY dataset_name ASC;
SELECT dataset_id, dataset_name FROM training_datasets WHERE dataset_size > 1000 ORDER BY dataset_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM training_datasets WHERE dataset_format = 'CSV' AND dataset_size < 5000;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_datasets FROM training_datasets;
SELECT dataset_name, dataset_size FROM training_datasets WHERE experiment_id = 5;
SELECT AVG(dataset_size) AS avg_size FROM training_datasets;
SELECT * FROM dataset;
SELECT name, description FROM dataset WHERE id = 1;
SELECT id, model_name, accuracy FROM experiment ORDER BY accuracy DESC;
SELECT * FROM dataset WHERE description IS NOT NULL;
SELECT COUNT(id) AS num_experiments FROM experiment;
SELECT id, name, description, created_at FROM dataset WHERE id = 1;
SELECT model_name, accuracy, loss, created_at FROM experiment WHERE accuracy > 0.8;
SELECT id, name, description, created_at FROM dataset ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT model_name, accuracy, loss, created_at FROM experiment ORDER BY accuracy DESC, created_at ASC;
SELECT id, name, description, created_at FROM dataset WHERE name LIKE 'A%';
SELECT * FROM training_dataset;
SELECT dataset_name, num_records FROM training_dataset WHERE created_on > '2021-01-01';
SELECT model_id, model_name, model_type, trained_on FROM deep_learning_model WHERE accuracy > 0.9;
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_name, start_time, end_time FROM experiment ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT dataset_name, num_records, created_on FROM training_dataset WHERE num_records > 10000;
SELECT * FROM training_dataset WHERE num_records > 100 ORDER BY created_on DESC;
SELECT dataset_name, num_records FROM training_dataset WHERE dataset_name LIKE 'A%' AND num_records BETWEEN 50 AND 200;
SELECT model_name, model_type, accuracy FROM deep_learning_model WHERE accuracy > 0.8 ORDER BY model_name;
SELECT experiment_name, start_time, end_time FROM experiment WHERE start_time > '2022-01-01' AND end_time < '2022-06-30';

SELECT td.dataset_name, dl.model_name, e.experiment_name FROM training_dataset td JOIN experiment e ON td.dataset_id = e.dataset_id JOIN deep_learning_model dl ON e.model_id = dl.model_id WHERE dl.accuracy > 0.75 ORDER BY e.end_time ASC;
SELECT * FROM training_datasets;
SELECT dataset_id, dataset_name FROM training_datasets WHERE dataset_size > 1000;
SELECT dataset_id, dataset_description FROM training_datasets WHERE dataset_name LIKE 'Data%';
SELECT * FROM experiments WHERE experiment_status = 'completed';
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_name FROM experiments WHERE experiment_status != 'failed';
SELECT * FROM training_datasets;
SELECT dataset_name, dataset_description FROM training_datasets WHERE dataset_size > 100;
SELECT * FROM experiments WHERE experiment_status = 'completed';
SELECT experiment_name, result_metrics FROM experiments INNER JOIN experiments_results ON experiments.experiment_id = experiments_results.experiment_id;
SELECT log_date, log_message FROM experiment_logs ORDER BY log_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM dataset;
SELECT dataset_name, dataset_description FROM dataset WHERE dataset_id = 1;
SELECT model_name, model_type, model_accuracy FROM model WHERE model_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM experiment WHERE experiment_id BETWEEN 2 AND 5;
SELECT training_id, model_id, epochs_trained, validation_accuracy FROM training_history ORDER BY epochs_trained DESC;
SELECT * FROM dataset ORDER BY dataset_name DESC, dataset_id ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT dataset_id, dataset_name, dataset_size FROM dataset INNER JOIN experiment ON dataset.dataset_id = experiment.dataset_id WHERE experiment.model_id = 3 AND dataset.dataset_size > 1000;
SELECT model_name, model_accuracy, model_type FROM model WHERE model_accuracy >= 0.8 ORDER BY model_accuracy DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT experiment.experiment_name, model.model_name, hyperparameters.learning_rate FROM experiment INNER JOIN model ON experiment.model_id = model.model_id INNER JOIN hyperparameters ON model.model_id = hyperparameters.model_id WHERE hyperparameters.learning_rate < 0.001;

SELECT dataset.dataset_name, experiment.experiment_name, training_history.epochs_trained FROM dataset INNER JOIN experiment ON dataset.dataset_id = experiment.dataset_id INNER JOIN training_history ON experiment.model_id = training_history.model_id;
